                Messiae Maximae iuveni infelicissi<lb break="no" n="2"/>mae inmatura morte praereptae quae <lb n="3"/><surplus>quae</surplus> vixit annos XXVI Primitivi<supplied reason="lost">u</supplied>s Senili<lb break="no" n="4"/>anus filius et Messius Maxumus <note>sic</note> frater <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>aciendum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>uraverunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Mehrere, teils aneinanderpassende Fragmente erhalten. Autopsie R. Wiegels.</p>
